  "title": "3-6 months Contract Office Adminstrator ($3500) #HJO",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong><br />• Plan, coordinate, and deliver office improvement and relocation projects<br />• Liaise with consultants and contractors, oversee project governance, and support workplace transformation initiatives<br />• Organize and conduct engagement sessions, briefings, and workplace feedback surveys<br />• Use digital tools (videos, infographics, visuals, etc.) to support communications and staff engagement<br />• Manage end-to-end project delivery, ensuring timelines, quality, and objectives are met</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />• Diploma or Degree in Project Management, Business, Communications, or related field<br />• Minimum 1–3 years of relevant experience in office projects roles<br /></p><p>Interested candidates are invited to email your resume to:</p><p>jen.ooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Jenalyn Ooi Huai Sian (R1765551)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p><p><br /></p>",
